des:
Filled with tips, traps, thoughts, and exercises on happiness, the Your Happiness Now Skill from Dr. Cathy Greenberg is a compilation of her decade of work in studying and helping Companies, coaches, women and working mothers be happy.

Listen as Dr. Cathy walks you through basic and advanced exercises. Find out about all the resources Dr. Cathy has available.

It's everything you need to start your journey now.Don't delay your happiness another day, get this app and get going!
